  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the study is to evaluate change in insulin secretory capacity in patients
      with type 2 diabetes mellitus as determined by hyperglycemic clamp after a 28-day oral
      administration of DS-8500a at 75 mg in a placebo-controlled, 2 × 2 crossover study. In
      addition, safety of this regimen will be examined in this study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
